<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
	<head>
		<meta charset="utf-8">
		<script src="https://code.jquery.com/jquery-latest.js"></script>
		<script>
			$(document).ready(function(){
				$("input").keypress(function(){
					var colors = ["navy", "blue", "yellow", "white", "green","maroon","teal","lime","purple"];
					var rand = colors[Math.floor(Math.random() * colors.length)];
					$(this).css("background-color", rand);
				});
			});
		</script>
	</head>
	<body>
		Вводите текст в это поле и оно будет менять свой цвет: <input type="text" name="changecolor" size="50">
	</body>
</html>
